      <description>To connect your Google account to Notion, start by navigating to the Notion settings page and clicking on &amp;lsquo;Google Drive&amp;rsquo; or &amp;lsquo;Google Calendar&amp;rsquo; to authenticate your account, then follow the prompts to authorize access. This integration enables you to access Google Drive files and calendar events directly within Notion.</description>
